![Episode3.jpg](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1574637969658-QFJNLA7YQJBMMCCVQVCG/Episode3.jpg)

The guys at Major Issues review the 2009 Watchmen film based on the Watchmen miniseries created by Alan Moore. With the inclusion of the Watchmen in the DC Universe, the Clique asks the hard questions about Dr Manhattan, Ozymandias, and Rorschach in a recap that is sure to make Zack Snyder blush. This aint your grandpa's film review.

It is the **VERY FIRST EPISODE** of the Major Issues Podcast! Join the guys from ComicBook Clique as they talk the new Avengers trailer, and do a deep dive into the CW 4-night crossover Crisis on Earth X!

If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the one stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
